FBIS4-43877 "drweu121aa_94003" FBIS-WEU-94-121 Daily Report 22 Jun 1994 INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Butrus-Ghali Congratulates France on Rwanda Decision Butrus-Ghali Congratulates France on Rwanda Decision LD2206211594 Paris France-Inter Radio Network in French 2030 GMT 22 Jun 94 LD2206211594 Paris France-Inter Radio Network French BFN [Text] UN Secretary General Butrus Butrus-Ghali has congratulated France for its attitude just after the UNSC [UN Security Council] vote on the French intervention operation in Rwanda: [Begin Ghali recording] I would like to express my gratitude to the French Government for this extremely courageous initiative. This is a humanitarian initiative, leading a multinational force, during an interim period, and until such time when we will be able to finalize the composition of a UN force which will take over from this multinational force. [end recording]
